<p><strong>标题</strong>：泪膜破碎时间</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/think-cyan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4886286); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4886286&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663841" alt="Think cyan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4886286)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/think-cyan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4886286); return false;">Think cyan</a></span>，进入<a href="/think-cyan-s-personnel-file">念青的人事档案</a>查看该作者的更多作品。</p>
<p><strong>鸣谢</strong>：</p>
<p>十分感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4457426&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663841" alt="Enflowerz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4457426)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;">Enflowerz</a></span>进行的润色和校对。</p>
<p>十分感谢帮忙康草稿并捉虫的各位亲，Thank you very much♪(･ω･)ﾉ</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+30</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
